text:
When numerous doctors brushed me off, it was Dr Ng who found that I had a Coarctation of the Aorta and also needed a stent. He took the trouble to LISTEN to his patient despite baseline test showing normal reading.

It also helps that he is a bubbly person and importantly caring.
A very kind and caring doc and the staffs are friendly too.

Dr. Alvin is a great Doctor.
HIGHLY RECOMMENDED
